"We try to recycle as much as possible so that our production and management activities have the least possible impact on the environment", explains entrepreneur Miluše Ryznarová.
The IT company Enlogit from Ústí Region also thinks about the health of its employees and, with each laptop, offered them an ergonomic chair and keyboards; it also supports work from home and at its business events uses the catering services of a local sheltered company.
"In addition, we support the Persons in Need scholarship, which specifically helps the local Roma community", says Ondřej Suchý, a company representative.
The company Praní a čištění in the Karlovy Vary region is also well placed with a mention, whose employees receive special bonuses that are passed on to their pension funds.
